items.title: Confidence Booster
items.headline: Wake Up to a New YOU
objectives_summary: This course will reveal how you can find so much confidence inside yourself that you will be able to be the person you have always wanted to be and do the things you most want to do.
You will learn what true self-confidence is and how to nurture yourself so that you stop the habits that sabotage you and start building the mindset that will grow your self-confidence.

You'll learn some strategies for dealing with people with difficult behavior. Armed with this understanding and some strategies, you'll be in a much better position to take charge in these situations and guide them to a more favorable outcome.

items.title: Unravel Your Uniqueness
items.headline: Build an Unshakable Legacy
objectives_summary: How to influence society: You will identify the current ways that you are impacting society and gain insight on the qualities you need need to proactively cause a change regardless of wherever you are, your background and your socio-economic status.

Your childhood: You will relieve some of the moments that influenced your worldview to decide if it accompanies the pathway you want to follow. You will look into your cultural influences, uninstall the negatives while setting up a new one.

Family: You will get to examine the skills needed to run a home, reflect on the 3Fs that prevent you from serving your family, community and yourself. You will eliminate the dynamite that breaks a home.
